Employee Management System (Java | Swing | MySQL)

The Employee Management System (EMS) is a desktop-based application built using Java Swing, JDBC, and MySQL that allows organizations to efficiently manage employee records. This project demonstrates CRUD operations, database connectivity, UI development, and core Java concepts.

